Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:04.48,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:07.73,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,We're in the same class again this year, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:09.73,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:10.72,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:13.74,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm happy about it as long as you are, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.93,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, where'd he go off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.78,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey there! Well don't you just look chipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Aren't you just thrilled about being in Class 10 with all the troublemakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:33.32,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:41.14,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He isn't used to being separated from all his friends in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.44,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's the first time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:52.89,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... There's a petal in your hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's okay. I'll get it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:04.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:09.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What should I do{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:15.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I forgot who I was before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:19.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}The wind brushes my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Lullaby of Birdland
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:26.09,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Kicking the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:29.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}a frail shadow stretches on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:34.85,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It's like a neverending summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:40.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It feels like sneaking into a pool
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:45.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hey, let's just swim with our clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:46.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hop{\fncinnamon cake}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}A spiral of sensational temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:53.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Those beats that sting me are strange
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.95,0:01:57.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}They burn out and disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:59.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I'm fine with those crazy days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:02.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Swinging with such electric speed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.09,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Surround
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.80,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What's that dance called{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.80,0:02:07.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:17.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Don't go, it lingers on  in my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Melody is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}like a love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.14,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.21,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:45.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.82,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Y-You're cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.77,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,There's no way you didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:50.48,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.74,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You helped him get the ticket for the sleeper, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.31,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.20,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,He said to keep it a secret from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I actually had a nice trip because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:02.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.16,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.59,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,We should've decided the class rep by drawing lots in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.83,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,No kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:15.71,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard there's already been a fight in Class 10! {Great start to the new school year...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:19.04,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I'm just glad I wasn't put in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.23,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,So, is that the best the Boxing Club got to offer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I thought you had a little more spirit than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.68,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hi, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.30,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:40.07,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting on the first day of the new year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:43.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Just gettin' a little exercise...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.29,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,That was fun. Been too long since I had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.84,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:07.68,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What d'you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're gonna just go in with that banged-up face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.69,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Is it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:13.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:18.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry, but would you take this guy to the infirmary and patch him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,All right, go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.09,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu, he's in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:25.87,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It still hurts a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.06,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I should get over it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:39.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pain will go away and I should be able to smile and relax again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.89,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm going to submit it to the public exhibition this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.29,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's the one Sentaro modeled for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:51.86,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.76,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.67,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,You don't have to force yourself to give me feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't know much about art...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.62,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.82,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,That's a strange thing for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.87,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,After all, painting and jazz are relatively close cousins, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.76,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,A painting is created on a place called the canvas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:16.20,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,while jazz is created during a time called the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:20.88,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,It's like etching your living self into that place and time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.89,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.69,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I don't remember who said it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:28.51,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Junichi was talking about it when I went down to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.93,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs40\blur0.8\fad(356,350)\c&H000403&\fnlemon squeezy\b1\frx12\fry356\frz312.5\pos(536,366)}Fukahori \NYurika
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.53,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Everything he says is just so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.34,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I feel like I could talk to him about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:43.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I went to Tokyo during spring break...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:48.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And I dropped by Brother Jun's place, but he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.03,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Apparently, he hadn't been back for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:55.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,so there were letters just bursting out of his mail slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Someone said he might be staying over somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.34,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:05.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,One of those letters may have been pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.14,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I wonder where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.74,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Aren't you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:18.27,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Just put a little spit on cuts like these and they heal up fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.06,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,What'll you do if it gets infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.94,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,C'mon, close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.15,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.00,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.91,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're in the same class as Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:38.16,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,From now on, would you look after him more instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.56,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um, well, I'd better get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.34,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.17,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Glad I caught up with you before you left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.14,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Are those tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.93,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,This glob looks like a tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.06,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,That's the tear of a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.46,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,In Greek mythology, the god Apollo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.57,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,fell in love with Daphne, the daughter of a river god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:09.32,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,He became obsessed and chased her everywhere, but she just wouldn't stop running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:12.66,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,At long last, she gave Apollo the ultimate rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.66,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,by turning herself into a bay laurel tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.91,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What unbearable heartbreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.58,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Such sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:23.21,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,He was so sick with grief that he fashioned a wreath out of the laurels!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:24.99,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.71,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.35,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,This is Matsuoka Seiji, a second-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:31.90,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,He's the Great Hope of East High's Art Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.02,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.74,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.97,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.48,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,We're both in Class 10, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.48,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Pleasure to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.52,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.65,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Do you remember that guy from last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' the chills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.70,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.83,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Are you free on our next day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.76,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I want to get you a gift as a thank you for doing me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:03.79,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:04.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.75,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot! Apollo, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like this guy would ever wear a wreath of laurels!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu, do you have detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.16,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.84,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I forgot to do my math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's unusual for someone as level-headed as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.86,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Who said I was level-headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.03,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm careless as can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:39.54,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I get more absent-minded in the spring. I better snap out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.96,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:44.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's from "The Sound of Music."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.04,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured you'd like that movie, Ritsu. {Who doesn't?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.66,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.89,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I wanted to, but before I knew it, it'd already stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.60,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I bet it was good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.06,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,How could I miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:05.31,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess I thought I'd be able to see it anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.80,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'm pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.32,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What is that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.22,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,"My Favorite Things."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, better not... I had my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.02,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there was somethin' I wanted your advice on, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,About my date...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,With Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.12,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:03.87,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well then, let me give some perfect advice to a romantic novice like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.51,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Huh?! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:14.89,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,If it's just the two of you, you're guaranteed to freeze up and blow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.65,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,D-Don't you make fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I can handle a date. Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.58,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:25.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You really think you can mind your P's and Q's in front of such a refined lady and behave like an adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.02,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,P-P's and Q's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.36,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,But for your own sake, you'd better not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.42,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,P's and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez, what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.84,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish everyone would just stop falling in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:53.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}That dope! Fine then, don't blame me for what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.43,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Sentaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:08.73,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,don't hold back. Tell me if you see something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:09.92,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:14.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I never get expensive stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.44,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Even this jacket is a hand-me-down from Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.74,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:25.39,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}And from then on, all we talked about was Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:31.83,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}When Brother Jun was in high school, nobody was cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.82,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,He was good at fightin', real smart too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.87,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.55,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had a good time talkin' about 'im,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now all I got left is a feelin' of emptiness in the pit of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:46.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Did your date go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.58,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,C-Course it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:53.06,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,A date is a piece of cake for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.25,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It didn't go well at all, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Just like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.37,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Stay away from her from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.08,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What's up with that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you really that dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:18.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Any way you look at it, you and a refined girl like that just don't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:21.14,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,She's just completely out of your league—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:28.35,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.48,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hi, Kawabuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:36.44,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.11,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I heard you went on a date with Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.53,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,She said she had a great time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.16,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,H-Hey, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.04,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Did she say anythin' else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.74,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You wanna know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.64,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Uh-huh! She said you were just so handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.87,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,and that maybe she'll even hold your hand next time! {DISGUSTING}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:58.34,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, Richie, you're here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.66,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna try playin' "My Favorite Things" with me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.73,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this? I thought he'd be mad at me for what I said at lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he seems to be in a great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.21,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.45,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I thought only jazz was allowed in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:30.45,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Oh, that kid with the mushroom cut, Matsuoka, forced it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.66,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I couldn't refuse, so I just carried it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.21,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.46,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.76,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Good for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,making a nice friend that lends you records...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.22,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey, Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.12,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Would you come upstairs a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.80,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What, did a new record come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.61,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Just come up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:54.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:58.43,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he actually gonna listen to that record?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I so anxious about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:07.91,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.42,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did you listen to the record I gave you yesterday? {penis inspection day?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.37,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Nah,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:15.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I can't get into music that has girls squealin' over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.03,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Isn't that the purpose of makin' music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.10,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna become popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.41,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't really care about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.85,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.73,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Well, I wanna be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.55,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hah? A star?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.56,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscy95\fs40\fnTooney Loons\b1\frz13.46\c&H272067&\pos(810,532)}Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.56,sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.3\bord0.6\fscy95\fs40\fnTooney Loons\b1\frz13.46\c&H2B2B61&\pos(810,532)}Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.42,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.51,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Are those the boxers of somebody who's aiming to be a star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.72,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:42.84,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.36,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,so if I don't stake my claim, they'll disappear in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.38,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,And we're poor, so we can't afford to buy new ones very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.82,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Amongst all my brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:53.36,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm called the "good-for-nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:55.37,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Honestly, singing is the only thing I'm good at...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:15:01.12,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I wanna prove that I can become somebody who's able to support his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.60,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,To me, this band is the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.42,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:11.63,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi, I need your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.78,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,A-Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.46,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,That was wonderful, Maruo! Much better than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.54,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:40.21,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,All right, now all we need is a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.14,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Seiji, are you at least gonna tell me who you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.66,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.12,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It'll be a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, Ri'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.14,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,No school tomorrow, so if you're free, wanna go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:15:59.02,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Ma told me to take the munchkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:03.27,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But lookin' after them alone is a tough job,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.21,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd ask you along to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.75,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, if you're busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:10.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.94,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:13.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,You free tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.79,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What d'you say we have us a clammin' contest at the beach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh? Clammin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:20.00,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Say, Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.78,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I like clamming, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:23.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.27,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:26.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Some kind of competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:34.06,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, Kaoru! Clamming means digging up clams at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.97,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh! It's confusing when this guy calls it a contest or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you going too, Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:40.59,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.43,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.54,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Then the threesome's set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.06,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,This is gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.86,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll need to mentally prepare myself this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}If those two have a romantic moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.36,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll casually get out of the way and just pray for Ritsu's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:16:59.91,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or that's the idea at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, maybe that's a non-issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.77,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I got a hamaguri clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:10.59,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,That's a short-necked clam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.09,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.30,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Fancy meeting you here, Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.13,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.36,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What cute little girls and boys. {STRANGER DANGER}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:21.43,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Y'know, there's a place over there where you can find a bunch of razor clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:22.27,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Razors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:24.96,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You must be Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.89,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I've heard about you from Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.24,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,She said you were exceptionally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are the razor clams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.08,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Oh, they're right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:35.96,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Follow me. {DON'T DO IT KIDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:40.55,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's with that guy? Sweet-talking everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.83,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Don't criticize the guy when you don't know 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.75,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Bro, you come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:46.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.94,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Nifty, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.12,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Who wants to try it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:57.70,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:58.42,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.05,Default,Taiichi,0,0,0,,Salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.93,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Looks like they're having a good time over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.62,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Should we join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,For some reason, that Matsuoka character rubs me the wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.15,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Taiichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:15.32,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.85,Default,Taiichi,0,0,0,,Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.99,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You were just surprised that the crab pinched you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:23.76,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Thank goodness that's all it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.84,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Hey, Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.09,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Don't tell me your drummer is Kawabuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.48,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Please, anybody but him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.21,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,I-I'm against it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.30,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,He isn't as scary as you think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.72,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,All I have to do is set him free from what's tying him down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.39,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,and then everything should work out the way I want it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Hey, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Catchin' any short-necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:57.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Better not underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm good at this kind of simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.53,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Well, I ain't gonna lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.45,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Clammin' contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:07.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What do I get if I win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,How about the record that Ritsu's dad gave you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.34,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Forget about it! 'Cause I'm gonna win anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.96,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What about the Beatles record?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.19,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kawabuchi, did you listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.72,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Wasn't bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:27.16,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did it stir up your interest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.66,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:29.85,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.76,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm thinkin' I'll help you out with
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,that band you're gonna have for the school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.43,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.50,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You'll join my rock band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.08,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:39.95,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.14,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.66,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.28,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna be away 'til the festival's over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:49.50,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,350)}We're just gonna be apart for a little while, Nishimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.46,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(150,150)}Let's send each other letters, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.42,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.63,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I was wrong about you, traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:05.15,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:08.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't wanna listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:18.69,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.12,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.66,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I acted like an angry little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:36.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}But being separated from him scares the hell out of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.67,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I abandoned him without even thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:46.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I came here, I'd forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.60,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I'm not any good at getting along with other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.08,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, I've made it this far, all on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:06.07,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.19,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Tsutomu, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.62,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Look at the end of the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.09,ED,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I waited for you on that road downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:41.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}Our promise to meet after school always held a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:51.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I was weak and distorted, and seemed to easily crack under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:22:03.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}You were the one who gave me wings then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:12.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I wish I could say I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:23.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}while you're looking for a faint light in the sky at dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.86,0:22:35.54,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}The letter I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:43.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}will never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:49.05,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}and nothing will ever change
